参考文章 ：得到脚本

```
from PIL import Image
im=Image.open('misc51.png')
im = im.convert('RGB')
img = Image.new("RGB",(900,150))

dic = {}

for h in range(900):
    for w in range(150):
        s = im.getpixel((h,w))
        dic[s] = dic.get(s,0)+1
lt = list(dic.items())
lt.sort(key = lambda x:x[-1])
print(lt)
```

