> shellcraft

下载题目附件pwn，丢进虚拟机checksec

![](/images/Pasted image 20250117145918.png)

是32位的，丢进ida反编译

```c
int __cdecl main(int argc, const char **argv, const char **envp)
{
  setvbuf(stdin, 0, 1, 0);
  setvbuf(stdout, 0, 2, 0);
  puts(asc_80486E0);
  puts(asc_8048754);
  puts(asc_80487D0);
  puts(asc_804885C);
  puts(asc_80488EC);
  puts(asc_8048970);
  puts(asc_8048A04);
  puts("    * *************************************                           ");
  puts(aClassifyCtfsho);
  puts("    * Type  : Linux_Security_Mechanisms                               ");
  puts("    * Site  : https://ctf.show/                                       ");
