## PWN105

```
char *__cdecl ctfshow(char *s)
{
  char dest[8]; // [esp+7h] [ebp-11h] BYREF
  unsigned __int8 v3; // [esp+Fh] [ebp-9h]

  v3 = strlen(s);
  if ( v3 <= 3u || v3 > 8u )
  {
    puts("Authentication failed!");
    exit(-1);
  }
  printf("Authentication successful, Hello %s", s);
  return strcpy(dest, s);
}
```

