```sql
SELECT ... INTO OUTFILE 'file_name'
        [CHARACTER SET charset_name]
        [export_options]
 
export_options:
    [{FIELDS | COLUMNS}
        [TERMINATED BY 'string']
        [[OPTIONALLY] ENCLOSED BY 'char']
        [ESCAPED BY 'char']
    ]
    [LINES
        [STARTING BY 'string']
        [TERMINATED BY 'string']
    ]
```

可以利用 export_options 插 shell。  
