# web入门：27常用姿势

https://fushuling.com/index.php/2023/08/20/ctfshow%E5%88%B7%E9%A2%98%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%AD/

